---
// About.astro - Static component for the about section
---

<section id="about">
	<div class="about-content">
		<h2>Hey There...</h2>
		<p class="intro">
			I'm Sam. Whether it's gaming or climbing boulders with friends, I find the most joy in competitive, high-pressure problem-solving.
			<br><br>I center my work around professionalism, collaboration, and enterprise satisfaction.
		</p>
</section>

<style>
	#about {
		background: #ffffff;
	}

	.about-content {
		max-width: 780px;
	}

	#about h2 {
		margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
	}

	.intro {
		font-size: 1.05rem;
		line-height: 1.7;
		color: #4b5563;
		margin-bottom: 2rem;
	}

	.coursework,
	.tools {
		margin-top: 1.75rem;
	}

	.coursework h3,
	.tools h3 {
		font-size: 0.95rem;
		letter-spacing: 0.08em;
		text-transform: uppercase;
		color: #6b7280;
		margin-bottom: 0.65rem;
		font-weight: 600;
	}

	.coursework p,
	.tools p {
		font-size: 1rem;
		line-height: 1.7;
		color: #4b5563;
	}
</style>
